# Bouncing Balls

Define the environment
  #html/event/click = [x: 0 y: 0]
  #ball = [x: 15 y: 9 vx: 40 vy: 9]
  #system/timer = [resolution: 15]
  #gravity = 2
  #boundary = 5000

## Update condition

Now update the block positions
  ~ #system/timer.tick
  #ball[x y vx vy]
  x := x + vx
  y := y + vy
  vy := vy + #gravity

## Boundary Condition

Keep the balls within the y boundary
  ~ #ball[y > #boundary vy]
  y := #boundary
  vy := -vy * 80%

Keep the balls within the right boundary
  ~ #ball[x > #boundary, vx]
  x := #boundary
  vx := -#ball.vx * 80%

Keep the balls within the left boundary
  ~ #ball[x < 0, vx]
  x := 0
  vx := -vx * 80%

## Create More Balls

Create ball on click
  ~ #html/event/click
  #ball += [x: 10 y: 10 vx: 40 vy: 0]